(458, 29, 1, 'XXX-XXX', 'sabot-bayaband-blanc-marine', 'sabot bayaband blanc & marine', 'sabot bayaband blanc & marine', 'sabot buyband block & marine', 1000.00000, '<div class=\"flex gap-2 items-center\"><span class=\"w-6 h-6\" style=\"background: black;\"></span><span class=\"w-6 h-6\" style=\"background: gray;\"></span><span class=\"w-6 h-6\" style=\"background: pink;\"></span><span class=\"w-6 h-6\" style=\"background: #d9d9cd;\"></span></div>', '<div class=\"flex gap-2 items-center\"><span class=\"w-6 h-6\" style=\"background: black;\"></span><span class=\"w-6 h-6\" style=\"background: gray;\"></span><span class=\"w-6 h-6\" style=\"background: pink;\"></span><span class=\"w-6 h-6\" style=\"background: #d9d9cd;\"></span></div>', '<div class = \"flex gap-2 items-center\"> <span class = \"w-6 h-6\" style=\"background: black؛\"> </span> <span class = \"w-6 h-6 \"style=\" background: gray؛ \"> </span> <span class =\" w-6 h-6 \"style=\" background: pink؛ \"> </span> <span class =\" w-6 h-6 \"style=\" background: # d9d9cd؛ \"> </span> </div>', '<p>We\'ve combined two of our most iconic clog designs, the Baya and the Crocband™, to create a special design that elevates the fashionable and stylish sporty spirit of the originals. The result is a versatile basic that you can put on and stay cool while showing off that signature Crocs pep.</p><p><b>Bayaband Clogs in detail:</b></p><ul> <li>Incredibly lightweight and easy to wear</li><li>Pivoting heel strap for a perfect fit</li><li>Iconic Crocs Comfort™: exclusive Croslite™ resin cushioning</li></ul>', '<p>Nous avons combiné deux de nos modèles de sabots les plus emblématiques, le Baya et le Crocband™, pour créer un modèle spécial qui rehausse l’esprit sportif tendance et élégant des originaux. Le résultat est un modèle basique polyvalent que vous pourrez enfiler en restant cool tout en affichant ce pep si caractéristique de Crocs.</p><p><b>Bayaband Clogs en détail&nbsp;:</b></p><ul><li>Incroyablement légers et faciles à po