(478, 1, 1, 'TO-2000', 'ampera-e-electric-operating-table', 'ampera-e electric operating table', 'table d’operation electrique opera-e', 'طاولة التشغيل الكهربائية ampera-e', 1000.00000, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p><span style=\"font-size:12px\">This electric operating table is suitable for surgery on the head, neck, thorax,<br />abdomen, perineum and extremities. It is also suitable for gynecological, obstetrical,<br />urological, ENT and orthopedic operations.<br />The table is height adjustable, tilts laterally, the backrest is tiltable, also equipped with the system<br /> Trendelenburg & reverse Trendelenburg tilt. All these functions are controllable via remote control.</span></p><p><span style=\"color:#008080\"><strong>Main Technical Parameters:</strong></span></p>< table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px\"><tbody><tr><td>Table Length<strong>2100 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Table width<strong>480 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Adjustable height<strong>750-1000 mm</strong></td> </tr><tr><td>Headrest<strong>280x325 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Backrest<strong>500x480 mm</strong></td>< /tr><tr><td>Seat<strong>530x480 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Leg section<strong>510x236 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Footrest<strong>180x273 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Lumbar section<strong>100x480 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Max. Capacity<strong>250kg</strong></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style=\"color:#008080\">< strong>Technical Setup:</strong></span></p><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px\"><tbody><tr><td >Remote control<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Headrest<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Anesthesia hoop<strong >1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Body Support<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Body Support shoulder<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Armrest<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Kickstand for knee support<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Cushion<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td> Straps (optional)<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Handle<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr></tbody> </table><p><span style=\"color:#008080\"><strong>Electrical Parameters:</strong></span></p><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing= \"1\" style=\"width:250px\"><tbody><tr><td>Movement speed<strong>4~16mm/s</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Hint Protection<strong>IPX4</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Power supply<strong>AC220V,50Hz</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Source internal electrical<strong>DC 24V</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Battery capacity:<br /><span style=\"font-size:11px\" ><strong>>2.4AH, security type for device: IB</strong></span></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style=\"color :#008080\"><strong>Setting sections:</strong></span></p><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px\">< tbody><tr><td>Reverse Trendelenburg:<strong>>20°</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Trendelenburg:<strong>>15°</strong></td ></tr><tr><td>Side tilt:<strong>> 15°</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Headrest raised from horizontal:<strong >> 45°</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Headrest lowered from horizontal:<strong>> 90°</strong></td></tr> <tr><td>Leg section lowered from horizontal:<strong>>90°</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Leg section open:<strong>>90° </strong></td></tr><tr><td>Backrest raised from horizontal<strong>> 45°</strong></td></tr><tr><td> Backrest lowered from horizontal<strong>> 15°</strong></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size:12px\">Cette table d’opération électrique est adaptée pour des interventions chirurgicales au niveau de la tête, cou, thorax,<br />abdomen, périnée et des extrémités. Elle est également adaptée aux opérations gynécologiques, obstétriques,<br />urologiques, ORL, ainsi qu’orthopédiques.<br />La table est réglable en hauteur, inclinable latéralement, le dossier est inclinable, également munie du système<br />d’inclinaison Trendelenburg &amp; Trendelenburg inversé. Toutes ces fonctions sont contrôlables via télécommande.</span></p><p><span style=\"color:#008080\"><strong>Paramètres Techniques Principaux:</strong></span></p><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px\"><tbody><tr><td>Longueur Table<strong>2100 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Largeur Table<strong>480 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Hauteur réglable<strong>750-1000 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Repose tête<strong>280x325 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Dossier<strong>500x480 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Assise<strong>530x480 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Section jambe<strong>510x236 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Repose pied<strong>180x273 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Section lombaire<strong>100x480 mm</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Capacité Max.<strong>250kg</strong></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style=\"color:#008080\"><strong>Configuration Technique:</strong></span></p><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px\"><tbody><tr><td>Télécommande<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Repose tête<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Arceau d’anesthésie<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Support du corps<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Support d’épaule<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Accoudoir<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Béquille pour supporter le genou<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Coussin<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sangles (en option)<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Poignée<strong>1 pc</strong></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span style=\"color:#008080\"><strong>Paramètres Electriques :</strong></span></p><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\" style=\"width:250px\"><tbody><tr><td>Vitesse des mouvements<strong>4~16mm/s</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Indice de Protection<strong>IPX4</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Alimentation<strong>AC220V,50Hz</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Source électrique interne<strong>DC 24V</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Capacité de la batterie :<br /><span style=\"font-size:11px\"><strong>&gt