(481, 1, 1, 'XOhaM694', 'electric-operating-table-astra-e-sk', 'electric operating table astra-e sk', 'table opération electrique astra-e sk', 'طاولة التشغيل الكهربائية astra-e sk', 1000.00000, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The<span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><strong>A100-4</strong></span>operating table is suitable for different types of surgical operations: chest surgery, abdomen, perineum, lower limbs, gynecology, urology, ENT, as well as neurosurgery.</p><p>All functions are controlled with a remote control and can be locked.</p><p>All sections have an X-ray cassette for radiological examination.</p><p>The operating table is equipped with a high performance built-in battery to guarantee operation for up to 80 operations.</p><p><span style=\"color:#B22222\"><strong>Dimensions:</strong></span></p><p>•Length of table top: 2070mm</p><p>•Width of table top: table: 550mm</p><p>•Minimum height: 700mm</p><p>•Maximum height: 1000mm</p><p>•battery life:<strong><u>from 30 to 50 operations by function</u></strong></p><p><span style=\"color:#B22222\"><strong>Movements:</strong></span></p><p>•Trendelenburg /Trendel reverse enburg: 25°/25°</p><p>•Side tilt: 15°/15°</p><p><span style=\"color:#B22222\"><strong>Section adjustment:< /strong></span></p><p>•Adjustable headrest: 45° /90°</p><p>•Adjustable backrest: 75° / 20°</p><p>•Adjustable leg section : 15°/ 90°</p><p>•Rotation Leg section: 90°</p><p>•Liftable lumbar section: 120 mm</p><p>•Longitudinal translation: 300 mm</p> <p>- Mains supply:</p><p style=\"margin-left:106.2pt\">• Supply voltage220V±22V</p><p style=\"margin-left:106.2pt\">•Frequency50Hz ±1Hz</p><p style=\"margin-left:106.2pt\">•Input power 600VA</p><p><span style=\"color:#B22222\"><strong>Accessories supplied:</strong></span></p><p>• Armrests (2pcs)<br />• Shoulder Support (2pcs)<br />• Leg Support (2pcs)<br />• Stirrups (2pcs)< br />• Anesthesia arm (1pc)<br />• Remote control (1pc)</p>', '<p>La table d\'opération<span style=\"color:#FF0000\"><strong>A100-4</strong></span>