(547, 4, 65, 'XOhaM290', 'dinamap-surveillance-monitor-3-parameters-temperature', 'dinamap surveillance monitor 3 parameters + temperature', 'dinamap moniteur de surveillance 3 parametres +température', 'dinamap surveillance monitor 3 parameters + درجة الحرارة', 1000.00000, NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>The Dinamap<strong><span style=\"color:#FF0000\">CMS5100-3</span></strong>is a 3-parameter monitoring monitor, which has the function of:</p><ul> <li>• Blood pressure measurement (systolic and diastolic)</li><li>•Display of the average blood pressure measurement;</li><li>•SPO2 monitoring;</li><li>•Heart rate monitoring;</li><li>•Temperature measurement.</li></ul><p><strong><u>Features:</u ></strong></p><ul><li>•LCD screen: 2.8 inch TFT Color LCD;</li><li>•Rechargeable battery with an autonomy of more than 3<strong>h</strong>at full charge;</li><li>•Ergonomic with direct access to the main functions;</li><li>•Compact, internal or external use (ambulance);</li><li>•Source Power supply: Built-in rechargeable Lithium battery, DC/AC for continuous monitoring;</li><li>•Large data storage capacity on internal memory;</li><li>•Alarm function (sound and visual lle), min. and max. configurable;</li><li>•Recording of blood pressure and SPO2 data;</li><li>•Data download to PC for analysis and printing of data;</li><li>•More than 2000 shots blood pressure measurement / more than 7800 SPO2 data;</li><li>•Dimensions: 190 x 162 x 240mm</li></ul><p><strong><u>Technical Specifications:</u> </strong></p><p><strong>NIBP</strong></p><ul><li>•Measurement method: Oscillometric</li><li>•Mode: Manual/ AUTO/ Continuous </li><li>•Measuring interval in continuous mode: 5 min</li><li>•Protection against possible overpressure: software and hardware</li><li>•Measuring range: 10 ˜ 270 mmHg</li><li>•Accuracy: max. mean ± 5 mmHg; maximum standard deviation = 8 mmHg</li></ul><p><strong>SpO2</strong></p><ul><li> • Continuous monitoring (in real time): SpO2, PR, Plethysmogram Spo, bar graph…</li><li>•Measuremen